data.description: Welcome to your cozy retreat, a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled into a well established community in the ever-growing, bustling Fayetteville, NC. From the sunken living room with the electric fireplace, to the new LVP found in the primary bedroom to the screened porch where many get togethers or a quiet summer evenings can be enjoyed, this home boasts character in every corner and is where laughter and memories await. Enjoy the convenience of location with a short commute to shopping centres, restaurants, Fort Liberty, 1-95, 295, and surrounding towns.
